---ability_Shell Pulse Enhanced---
Bullet Definition :: [[shellpulseenhanced]]
VFX Cast :: trigger:Shell*

---bulletdef_shellpulseenhanced---
sprite Custom10
color 2
potency 100
repeat bullets:48 speed:4 angle:0 maxAngle:360 delay:1 directionType:absolute
	wait 100
	vanish
wait 20
sprite Custom11
color 2
potency 115
repeat bullets:24 speed:6 angle:7.5 maxAngle:360 delay:3 directionType:absolute
	wait 80
	vanish

---ability_Turtle Barrage---
Bullet Definition :: [[turtlebarrage]]
VFX Cast :: trigger:Attack*

---bulletdef_turtlebarrage---
sprite Custom11
color 4
potency 100
nway speed:10 bullets:5 spread:40 angle:0.0 directionType:relative
wait 3
nway speed:10 bullets:7 spread:30 angle:-10.0 maxAngle:10.0 directionType:relative
wait 3
nway speed:12 bullets:3 spread:20 angle:0.0 directionType:relative

